622
00:36:24,269 --> 00:36:27,070
Nikdo tady nemá stejnou barvu!

623
00:36:27,309 --> 00:36:29,590
Gu Wei Yi má na sobě žlutou.

624
00:36:29,869 --> 00:36:31,389
<i>Jiný odstín, ale je žlutá!

625
00:36:31,789 --> 00:36:32,909
<i>- To je pravda!
- Jo, je žlutá!

626
00:36:32,909 --> 00:36:38,049
Pohled do očí!

627
00:36:38,389 --> 00:36:40,670
Mo Mo, dáš radši fant?!

628
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:41,510
Pospěš si!

629
00:36:41,789 --> 00:36:42,389
Jdi na to,

630
00:36:42,909 --> 00:36:44,429
časovač je připraven!

631
00:36:44,869 --> 00:36:45,829
Mo Mo,

632
00:36:46,309 --> 00:36:48,509
že ty se bojíš?

633
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,190
Vůbec ne?

634
00:36:50,550 --> 00:36:51,610
Nebojím se Gu Wei Yiho!

635
00:36:51,869 --> 00:36:53,349
Ani trošku!

636
00:36:53,789 --> 00:36:54,730
<i>No tak!

637
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:58,470
<i>Start!

638
00:37:03,550 --> 00:37:04,310
<i>17

